   {"instruction": "Unscrew the bolts. Hold the nut underneath while turning the bolt from the top.", "safety_tip": "If bolts are corroded, apply penetrating oil and wait 10 minutes."},
   {"instruction": "Remove old seat and clean the mounting area.", "safety_tip": "Use disinfectant — this area accumulates grime."},
   {"instruction": "Place the new seat, insert bolts, and tighten evenly.", "safety_tip": "Don''t overtighten — you can crack the porcelain."}]',
