   {"instruction": "Loosen the slip nuts on both ends of the P-trap by hand or with pliers.", "safety_tip": "Turn counterclockwise to loosen."},
   {"instruction": "Remove the P-trap and dump contents into the bucket.", "safety_tip": "Wear rubber gloves — drain sludge is unpleasant."},
   {"instruction": "Clean the inside with a bottle brush and hot water.", "safety_tip": "Inspect washers — replace if cracked or compressed."},
   {"instruction": "Reinstall and hand-tighten slip nuts, then snug with pliers.", "safety_tip": "Run water and check for leaks at both connections."}]',
 'green', 'If the pipe itself is cracked or corroded.', '$0-5',
 ARRAY['clean P-trap', 'P-trap cleaning', 'sink P-trap', 'smelly drain', 'clean drain trap']),

