   {"instruction": "Connect new hoses — hot to hot, cold to cold. Hand-tighten, then 1/4 turn with pliers.", "safety_tip": "Use braided stainless steel — rubber hoses are the #1 cause of home water damage."},
   {"instruction": "Turn on water slowly and check for leaks at all four connections.", "safety_tip": "Check again after one wash cycle."}]',
