   {"instruction": "Disconnect the two wires from the old button.", "safety_tip": "Don''t let the wires fall back into the wall — tape them temporarily."},
   {"instruction": "Connect the two wires to the new button (either terminal — no polarity).", "safety_tip": "Wrap bare wire clockwise around the screws."},
   {"instruction": "Mount the new button and test.", "safety_tip": "If the bell still doesn''t work, the transformer or chime unit may be the issue."}]',
