   {"instruction": "Apply gutter sealant to any seam leaks.", "safety_tip": "Clean and dry the area before applying sealant."},
   {"instruction": "Test with a garden hose to check flow and leaks.", "safety_tip": "Ensure gutters slope slightly toward downspouts (1/4 inch per 10 feet)."}]',
