   {"instruction": "Pull the old handle off the stem. If stuck, use a handle puller or work it gently.", "safety_tip": "Don''t force it — you can break the stem."},
   {"instruction": "Place the new handle on the stem, align, and secure with the screw.", "safety_tip": "Ensure the handle opens counterclockwise and closes clockwise (standard)."},
