   {"instruction": "For cracks wider than 1/2 inch, press backer rod into the crack first.", "safety_tip": "Backer rod allows the filler to flex without cracking."},
   {"instruction": "Apply concrete crack filler (caulk-tube type for narrow, self-leveling for wider).", "safety_tip": "Fill slightly below the surface for self-leveling; flush for caulk type."},
